org.cyclops.integrateddynamics.api.path

Interface IPathElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<IPathElement>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PartTypeConnector.State, PartTypeConnectorMonoDirectional.State, PartTypeConnectorOmniDirectional.State, PathElementCable, PathElementDefault, PathElementTile, PathElementTileMultipartTicking

    public interface IPathElement
extends java.lang.Comparable<IPathElement>
    An element that can be used to construct paths using the PathFinder. Multiple instances for the same 'element' can be created, so the comparator implementation must make sure that these instances are considered equal. These instances are used as a simple way of referring to these elements.
